title: Sunday Comics: What A Cute Rabbit!
text:
Hello! It’s time for Kotaku’s Sunday Comics, your weekly roundup of the best webcomics. The images enlarge if you click on the magnifying glass icon.

Corpse Run by Alex Di Stasi. Published October 17. Read more of Corpse Run.

Awkward Zombie by Katie Tiedrich. Published October 14. Read more of Awkward Zombie.

Clueless Hero by Luis Lee and Ana Gaby Perez. Published October 14. Read more of Clueless Hero.

Double XP by M.S. Corley and Josh Crandall. Published October 16. Read more of Double XP.

(No new comic this week.)

Life in Aggro by Fei Hsiao and Cecilia Vasquez. Originally published February 11, 2018. Read more of Life in Aggro.

Nerf NOW!! by Josué Pereira. Published October 19. Read more of Nerf NOW!!

Penny Arcade by Jerry Holkins and Mike Krahulik. Published October 15. Read more of Penny Arcade.
